
  Ludicolo    Water Type Pokémon

  LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon 
  as it hears cheerful, festive 
  music.  Ludicolo is said 
  to appear when it hears the singing 
  of children on hiking outings. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Lotad ► Lombre ► Ludicolo

